Title: See No Evil
Plot: A wife and a 9-year-old blind daughter of a Navy captain are kidnapped and the captain is a hostage in his own office, communicating with kidnappers, who watch his every step via computer camera.  NCIS team investigates the scheme where large amount of money is involved.
GuestStars: David Keith, William Mapother, Ely Pouget, Brian Dietzen, Audrey Wasilewski, Abigail Breslin
